  ('The_Lighthouse', 34, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   34  •   Team Retrospective:  <Confluence Reference>  •   Open Defects:  <JIRA/ALM Reference>  3.3.10   Bulk Provisioning Service : Behaviors : [POST/cards/batch]  •   Validations  o   bps - enr - val.001.enroll.validations.src - client - id.mandatory  o   bps - enr - val.002.enroll.validations.service - id.mandatory  o   bps - enr - val.003.enroll.validations.src - dpa - id.mandatory  o   bps - enr - val.004.enroll.validations.external - batch - id.mandatory  o   bps - enr - val.005.enroll.validations.bulk - provisioing - type.possible - values  o   bps - enr - val.006.enroll.validations.bulk - provisioing - type.mismatch  o   bps - enr - val.007.enroll.validations.external - consumer - id.format  o   bps - enr - val.008.enroll.validations.external - card - id.format  o   bps - enr - val.009.enroll.validations.linked - identities.structure  •   Defaults  o   bps - enr - def.001.enroll.defaults.bulk - provisioning - type  •   Conflicts  •   Business Logic  o   bps - enr - blo.001.enroll.business - logic.re - submitted - batch  •   KPI Events  •   Successful Requests  3.3.10.1   Validations  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  bps - enr -  val.001.enroll.validations.src -  client - id.mandatory  CURRENT  Reject batch  enrollment of  cards if  request is  without src -  client - id  Given   a request is  received for batch  enrollment of cards  When   request  doesn''t have src -  client - id  Then   reject the  entire batch request  and return the  response as 400 bad  request  1.   Initial  version  under  Project  Lighthouse  bps - enr -  val.002.enroll.validations.service -  id.mandatory  CURRENT  Reject batch  enrollment of  cards if  request is  Given   a request is  received for batch  enrollment of cards  1.   Initial  version  under  Project  Lighthouse'),
