  ('The_Lighthouse', 42, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   42  Endpoin  t  Purpos  e  Behaviors   KPI  Eve  nts  Sequ  ence  Diagr  am  Downstr  eam(s)  A  vg  T  P  S  Pe  ak  TP  S  Proje  cted  TPS  (2026  )  Avg  Resp  onse  Time  P90  Resp  onse  Time  it is  used for  retrievin  g  Payload  purpose  Confirm  ations  endpoin  t  T he  Confirm  ation  API  allows  the  Client  to notify  MACS  about  the  outcom  e of a  checko  ut order  or  paymen  t  authoriz  ation.  TF148816 :  (Endpoint:   POST   /api/c  onfirmations)  1   20   8.5ms   12.3m  s  Compos  ite  checkou  t  endpoin  t  Only  used by  Apple:  enrollm  ent and  Checko  ut is  consoli  dated  into one  single  endpoin  t, and  support  ing  batch  transact  ions.  TF148429 :  (Endpoint:   POST  /transaction/credentials/  ENROLL_AND -  CHECKOUT)  2   20   1.05s   1.93s  Guest  checkou  t  endpoin  t  38  0  1500   59ms   88ms'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 43, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   43  3.4.5   Service Capabilities and configurations  [DRAFT : Under Review] MACS Service Capability Configuration   -   Alberta   -   Confluence  https://scm.mastercard.int/stash/projects/ALBERTA/repos/config - repo -  be/browse/application.yml  3.4.6   High - Level Design Artifacts  •   ER Diagram :   Checkout Service ER Diagram  •   Component interaction   -   MACS Checkout  •   Data Model:   Checkout Redis DataModel   -   Alberta   -   Confluence  3.4.7   Current Performance Metrics  •   Metrics:   Reports   -   Alberta   -   Confluence  •   Monitoring:  o   Link to Dynatrace dashboards   -  ▪   C heckout:   https://zir47692.live.dynatrace.com/#dashboard;gtf= -  24h%20to%20now;gf=all;id=19f96598 - 68d0 - 47fa - b56…  ▪   Composite Checkout:  https://zir47692.live.dynatrace.com/#dashboard;gtf= -  24h%20to%20now;gf=all;id=6889b731 - 1728 - 4542 - 94a…  ▪   CDS :   https://zir47692.live.dynatrace.com/#dashboard;id=86dcf46b -  fd51 - 4f91 - 9f7a - e49078cdd74f;gtf= - 24h%20t…  ▪   MACS Service Availability  o   SRE Alerts  3.4.8   Technical Roadmap  •   Pathfinder Engineering Roadmap   -   Alberta   -   Confluence  3.4.9   Technical Infrastructure  Name   Link  Technica  l Asset  Details  https://sso.internal.eportal.mastercard.int/pgmctg - prod - portal/program - catalog -  ui/#/technical - assets/5453/details  Reposito  ry  https://scm.mastercard.int/stash/projects/ALBERTA/repos/checkout - service/browse  Postman  Collectio  n  https://scm.mastercard.int/stash/projects/ALBERTA/repos/postman - tests/browse/src -  checkout - service/c…'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 44, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   44  Name   Link  Oracle  Databas  e  https://confluence.mastercard.int/spaces/alberta/pages/2068531225/Checkout+Servi  ce+Domain+ - +Oracle+…  Secured  Access  Policy  https://scm.mastercard.int/stash/projects/SPMADMIN/repos/com - mastercard -  src_orchestration - checkout/…  Static  Code  Analysis  Tool  https://fusion.mastercard.int/sonar/dashboard?id=com.mastercard%3Acheckout -  service  Black  Duck  Scan  3.4.10   Team and ALM  •   Team:  Mastercard Checkout Services   -   Team Composition  •   ALM/Jira Current Iteration Status:  Pathfinder Dashboard   (log in using   youremployeeid@mastercard.com )  •   Prod Support Escalation:  Pathfinder Escalation   -   Alberta   -   Confluence  •   Iteration Planning Board:  •   Team ALM Board:  https://rally1.rallydev.com/#/192829782716d/iterationstatus  •   Open Defects:  3.4.11   Stage Environment'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 45, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   45  3.4.12   Checkout Service technical roadmap  Sr.  No.  Title   Description   Impact   Priority  1   Plain text PII data in  external_account_id  Previously, the profile service incorrectly  sent consumers'' email addresses in the  external_account field to the consumer  service for companion programs (when  Identity_Type was EMAIL). As this field  was not designed for PII, it stored these  emails in plain   text. The profile service  fixed the defect on their side and now  sends a null value when Identity_Type is  EMAIL, but existing plain text data remains  in the consumer domain and needs a  remediation.  This is  potential  compliance  violation if we  have PII in  plain stored  High  3.5   Consumer Service Dashboard  3.5.1   Table of Contents  •   Overview  •   Dependencies  •   Endpoints & behavior  o   Endpoints Overview  o   Directory 2.0 : Directory Consumer Endpoints  o   Directory 2.0 : Program Consumer Endpoints  o   Directory 2.0 : Consumer Manager Endpoints  •   High - Level Design Artifacts  •   Operational and Performance references  •   Technical Roadmap  •   Technical Infrastructure  •   Team and ALM  3.5.2   Overview  •   Description:  Consumer Service is a program - agnostic platform service within the MACS that manages  consumer profiles from creation to deletion. It oversees consumer verification, which will  transition to the authentication service, and handles consent management, keepin g  records of all consents given by consumers.  •   Purpose & Scope:  o   As a platform service, it delivers significant business value to MACS by  supporting various flows such as B2C (Click To Pay) and B2B (SCOF).'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 46, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   46  o   It also offers separate directories for each issuer, enhancing trust and  compliance. This allows issuers to securely onboard consumer data and  enables MACS to provide auto - enrolment solutions where issuers remain in  control of their data.  o   Additionally, the MACS supports third - party wallets (e.g. Samsung) by allowing  wallets to provision consumer and wallet information in the directory. This  enables the presentation of wallet credentials during a payment experience and  facilitates seamless l inking or redirection to the Wallet interface when a  consumer selects a wallet for payment.  3.5.3   Dependencies  This table lists and describes all services or systems that provide input or trigger events for this  microservice or rely on data or functionalities from this microservice.  Service Name   Type   Service Dashboard  Pre - Checkout   Upstream  Push Provisioning   Upstream  Profile   Upstream  Account Management Service   Upstream  Checkout   Upstream  Consumer Scheduler   Upstream  CaaS   Downstream  High Level Interactions'),
