  ('The_Lighthouse', 81, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   81  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  When   paginati  on limit or  offset are less  than zero  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  cns - mgr - sea - val.002.search -  consumer.validations.program -  group.mandatory  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  without program  group  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  When   request  is without  program group  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  1.   XID  story  referen  ce  cns - mgr - sea - val.003.search -  consumer.validations.program -  group.mandatory  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  without program  group  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  When   request  is without  program group  in case of any  search criteria  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  1.   XID  story  referen  ce  cns - mgr - sea - val.004.search -  consumer.validations.search - by - plain -  text - email  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  without plain text  email if email criteria  is opted  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  1.   XID  story  referen  ce'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 82, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   82  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  of search - by -  email  When   no plain  text is  included in the  request  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  cns - mgr - sea - val.005.search -  consumer.validations.search - by - plain -  text - mobile  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  without plain text  mobileWithCountryC  ode if mobile criteria  is opted  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  of search - by -  mobile  When   no plain  mobile - with -  country - code  is included in  the request  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  1.   XID  story  referen  ce  cns - mgr - sea - val.006.search -  consumer.validations.search - by -  multiple - pairs - of - hashed - email - and -  hashed - mobile - with - country - code  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  without any items in  the pair if pair criteria  is opted  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  of search - by -  hashed -  emails - and -  hashed -  mobiles  When   any pair  is included in  the request  without any  email and/or  mobile  1.   XID  story  referen  ce'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 83, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   83  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  cns - mgr - sea - val.007.search -  consumer.validations.search - by -  multiple - pairs - of - hashed - email - and -  hashed - mobile - with - country - code  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request  with more than two  items in the pair if  pair criteria is opted  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  of search - by -  hashed -  emails - and -  hashed -  mobiles  When   any pair  is included in  the request  but with more  than two  emails and/or  mobiles  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  1.   XID  story  referen  ce  cns - mgr - sea - val.008.search -  consumer.validations.search - by -  multiple - pairs - of - hashed - email - and -  hashed - mobile - with - country - code  PROPOSED  Support the search  consumer request  even with only one  item in the pair if pair  criteria is opted  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  of search - by -  hashed -  emails - and -  hashed -  mobiles  When   any pair  is included in  the request  with only one  item in the pair  Then   process  the request  successfully  1.   XID  story  referen  ce'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 84, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   84  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  without  rejection  cns - mgr - sea - val.009.search -  consumer.validations.search - by -  multiple - pairs - of - hashed - email - and -  hashed - mobile - with - country - code.limit  PROPOSED  Reject the search  consumer request if  number of pairs  exceeds the  configured limit  Given   a  search  consumer  request is  received in a  consumer  manager  using criteria  of search - by -  hashed -  emails - and -  hashed -  mobiles  When   number  of pairs  exceeds  the   configured  limit  Then   reject  the request  and return the  response as  400 bad  request  1.   XID  story  referen  ce  3.5.16.2   Defaults  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  cns - mgr - sea - def.001.search -  consumer.defaults.parameters.masked  PROPOSED  Consumer  search must  return only  masked  records by  default  Given   a search  consumer request  is received in a  consumer  manager  When   '' masked''  parameter is not  specified in  request  Then   consumer  response must  return PII data  only in masked  format without  plain text  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea - def.002.search -  consumer.defaults.parameters.include -  litigation - hold  PROPOSED  Consumer  search must  not return a  record by  default if  Given   a search  consumer request  is received in a  consumer  manager  1.   XID story  reference'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 85, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   85  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  consumer is  held up for  litigation  When '' include -  litigation - hold''  parameter is not  specified in  request   and  matching  consumer is held  up for litigation  Then   don''t return  a   consumer  record by default  3.5.16.3   Business Logic  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.001.search -  consumer.business -  logic.masked -  pagination - limit  PROPOSED  Search results  will consider the  separate  configured  pagination limit if  only masked  records are  requested  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager in masked  format only  When   requested pagination  limit exceeds the   configured  limit for masked configuration  Then   search results should be  returned to the extent of  configured limit of masked  configuration only and log the  warning  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.002.search -  consumer.business -  logic.unmasked -  pagination - limit  PROPOSED  Search results  will consider the  separate  configured  pagination limit if  unmasked  records are also  requested  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager in  unmasked format as well  When   requested pagination  limit exceeds the   configured  limit for unmasked  configuration  Then   search results should be  returned to the extent of  configured limit of unmasked  configuration only and log the  warning  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.003.search -  consumer.business -  logic.masking  PROPOSED  Consumer  search must  return PII data  only in masked  format  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When '' masked'' parameter is  sent as true  Then   consumer response  must return PII data only in  masked format without plain  text  1.   XID story  reference'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 86, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   86  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.004.search -  consumer.business -  logic.unmasking  PROPOSED  Consumer  search must  return PII data in  masked as well  as plain text  format  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When '' masked'' parameter is  sent as false  Then   consumer response  must return PII data in masked  format as well as in plain text  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.005.search -  consumer.business -  logic.with - litigation - hold  PROPOSED  Search a  consumer record  held up for  litigation  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When '' includeLitigationHold''  parameter is sent as true  Then   return consumer records  even if they are held up for  litigation  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.006.search -  consumer.business -  logic.without - litigation -  hold  PROPOSED  Search a  consumer record  held up for  litigation  Given   a get consumer request  is received in a consumer  manager  When '' includeLitigationHold''  parameter is sent as false  Then   don''t   return such records  which are held up for litigation,  only return those records  which are not held up for  litigation.  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.007.search -  consumer.business -  logic.unlocking  NA  Unlocking  consumer  accounts  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   consumer records are  locked  Then   unlock the those  consumer accounts whose  lock expiration time has  elapsed before being returned  in the response and don''t  unlock those consumer  accounts whose lock expiration  period has not elapsed  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.008.search -  consumer.business -  logic.non - existent -  account  PROPOSED  Attempt to  search a non  existent  consumers  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   no matching   consumer  records is not found in a  directory as per the search  criteria  Then   return the empty list in  the response without any error  1.   XID story  reference'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 87, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   87  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.009.search -  consumer.business -  logic.non - existent -  account  PROPOSED  Attempt to  search a non  existent  consumers  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   matching   consumer  records found in a directory as  per the search criteria but no  associated records are found  in a program group  Then   return the empty list in  the response without any error  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.010.search -  consumer.business -  logic.matching - records  PROPOSED  Search  consumers in a  program group  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   matching   consumer  records found in a directory as  per the search criteria but only  few of them are found  associated with a program  group  Then   return only those  consumers which are found in  directories and program group  both. Don''t return the records  which are found only in  directory and not in program  group  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.011.search -  consumer.business -  logic.search - by - plain -  email - in - program - group  PROPOSED  Search a  consumer with  plain email in  specified  program group  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   request is sent using  search criteria as plain email  and with program group  Then   search consumer with  plain email in all directories but  return only those consumer  records which are associated  with a given program group  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.012.search -  consumer.business -  logic.search - by - plain -  mobile - with - country -  code - in - program - group  PROPOSED  Search a  consumer with  plain mobile with  country code in  specified group  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   request is sent using  search criteria as plain mobile -  with - country - code and with  program group  Then   search consumer with  plain mobile with country code  in all directories but return only  those consumer records which  are associated with a given  program group  1.   XID story  reference'),
  ('The_Lighthouse', 88, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   88  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.013.search -  consumer.business -  logic.search - by -  multiple - pairs - of -  hashed - email - and -  hashed - mobile - with -  country - code - in -  program - group  PROPOSED  Search a  consumer with  the combination  of hashed email  and hashed  mobile with  country code in  specified  program group  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   request is sent using  search criteria as multiple  different pairs of combination  of hashed email and hashed  mobile with country code and  with program group  Then   search all consumer  records matching the criteria in  all directories. Consumer  records for each pair should be  searched independently and all  those matching consumer  records of each pair should be  considered in the results. Then  return only those consumer  records which are associated  with a given program group.  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.014.search -  consumer.business -  logic.pagination  PROPOSED  Pagination of  search result  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   consumer records are  found matching a search  criteria  Then   search results should be  paginated based based on limit  and offset parameters  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.015.search -  consumer.business -  logic.sorting  PROPOSED  Sorting of search  result  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   consumer records are  found matching a search  criteria  Then   search results should be  sorted based on creation date  time stamp in ascending order  1.   XID story  reference  cns - mgr - sea -  blo.016.search -  consumer.business -  logic.pagination  PROPOSED  completeness of  search result  Given   a search consumer  request is received in a  consumer manager  When   consumer records are  returned in a paginated fashion  Then   no record should be  duplicated and no record  should be missed across all  the pages  1.   XID story  reference  3.5.16.4   KPI Events'),
