  ('The_Lighthouse', 172, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   172  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  email address  not in RFC 822  format   -   is not  allowed  directory to  update identities  When   email  address is not in  RFC 822 format  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  referenc  e  dir - cns - upd - val.012.update - directory -  consumer.validations.identities.mobile -  format  PROPOSED  Consumer  update with  mobile number  which doesn''t  comply with  given regex  Given   a  consumer  creation request  is received in a  directory to  update identities  When   mobile  number doesn''t  comply  with   Regex  -   "^[0 - 9]{4,14}$"  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  1.   XID  story  referenc  e  dir - cns - upd - val.013.update - directory -  consumer.validations.identities.mobile -  country - code - format  PROPOSED  Consumer with  mobile country  code which  doesn''t comply  with given  regex  Given   a  consumer  update request is  received in a  directory  When   mobile  country code  doesn''t comply  with   Regex  -   "^[+]?[0 -  9]{1,4}$"  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  1.   XID  story  referenc  e  dir - cns - upd - val.014.update - directory -  consumer.validations.national - id  PROPOSED  Update to  National Id is  not allowed   if  disabled in  region - config -  library  Given   a  consumer  update request is  received in a  directory to  update national  id  When   national id  is configured as  not editable in  1.   XID  story  referenc  e'),
