  ('The_Lighthouse', 188, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   188  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  program  without  program - id  received in a  program  When   request  doesn''t have  program - id  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  pgm - cns - upd - val.002.update -  program -  consumer.validations.consumer -  id.mandatory  PROPOSED  Consumer in a  program cannot  be updated  without a  consumer - id  Given   a  consumer update  request is  received in a  program  When   request  doesn''t have a  consumer - id  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  1.   XID story  reference  pgm - cns - upd - val.003.update -  program -  consumer.validations.type.possible -  values  PROPOSED  Consumer in a  program can be  updated using  either program -  consumer - id or  directory -  consumer - id  only  Given   a  consumer update  request is  received in a  program  When   request  contains a type  anything other  than program -  consumer - id and  directory -  consumer - id  Then   reject the  request and  return the  response as 400  bad request  1.   XID story  reference  3.5.25.2   Defaults  Behavior Id   Title   Behavior   Change Log  pgm - cns - upd - def.001.update -  program -  consumer.defaults.parameters.type  PROPOSED  Consumer will  be updated  using  program -  Given   a consumer  update request is  received in a  program  When   '' type''  parameter is not  1.   XID story  reference'),
