  ('The_Lighthouse', 245, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  MACS Services   –   245  3.9.6   Service Level Agreements (SLAs)  •   Overview:  Detail the agreed performance metrics such as uptime, response time, and error  thresholds.  •   Documentation:  Provide links to formal SLA documents or dashboards for real - time monitoring.  3.9.7   Current Performance Metrics  •   Metrics:  Present current data including response times, throughput, error rates, etc.  •   Visualization:  o   Embed charts, graphs, or tables for visual representation.  •   Monitoring:   Link to dashboards or monitoring tools for further analysis.  o   PI_Service _Dashboard  o   PI - EPS_OutBound_APIGTW_Dashboard  3.9.8   Future Projections  •   Projections:  Outline expected future performance trends, capacity planning details, and predicted  growth.  •   Analytical Data:  Include historical performance data and forecasts to support the projections.  •   Impact Analysis:  Describe how anticipated changes might affect the overall system.  3.9.9   Technical Roadmap  •   Planned Enhancements:  List upcoming features, improvements, and architectural changes.  •   Timeline & Milestones:  Provide a timeline with key milestones and deadlines.  •   Dependencies & Risks:  Identify any dependencies or potential risks associated with the roadmap.  •   Documentation:  Include links to detailed project plans or roadmap documents if available.  •   Dynatrace reports  o   MACS PI - CORE Service Insights   -   Mastercard: zir47692   -   Production   -  Dynatrace   (per end point)  o   PI - EPS:   https://zir47692.live.dynatrace.com/#dashboard;gtf= -  24h%20to%20now;gf=all;id=e7b7d4d3 - af9e - 40cd - 8925 -  c9554a17665a;applyDashboardDefaults=true  3.9.10   Payment Instrument Service 1.0   -   Behaviors  Dir 1.0 Card Services Swagger  3.9.10.1   Payment Instrument Service 1.0 : Behavior : [POST /card/accountRange]  Retrieve account range details based on FPAN or Digital Card Id'),
