  ('The_Lighthouse', 278, 'Alberta   –   The Lighthouse  Programs and Products   –   278  •   Performs payment process after receiving transaction credentials from MACS  Actor   -   Issuer  •   Has to onboard BIN ranges to guest checkout tokenization program  •   Must support processing of DE48.. elements ??  •   Wil be able to see various indicators while processing payment authorization message  and can use it in authorization decisioning  o   55 M/N  o   CFEN  o   54 ??  Actor   -   Consumer  •   Choose to perform guest checkout on Merchant site not willing to store card information  on merchant site  •   Gets the goods after successful checkout and payment  5.7.4   Technical workflow  5.7.5   Customers  As of now India only  Customer Tracker   -   SRC Checkout Product Strategy   -   Confluence  5.7.6   Dashboards and statistics  5.7.7   Use cases  B2C New User   -   <<UX>>  o   C2PUC52   -   New User Flow  o   C2PUC53   -   New User Flow   -   BAI Flow (Billing address optional)  o   C2PUC54   -   New User Flow   -   Bulk Flow  o   C2PUC55   -   New User Flow   -   Bulk Flow & Mdes Idv  B2C Returning User   <<UX>>  o   C2PUC1 -   Consumer with C2P profile only performs checkout with an existing  card  o   C2PUC2   -   Consumer performs checkout with a new card  o   C2PUC3   -   Consumer with bulk profile performs a checkout with an un -  provisioned card  o   C2PUC4   -   Consumer with C2P profile performs a checkout with an   un -  provisioned card  o   C2PUC5   -   Consumer with ISD profile performs a checkout with an   un -  provisioned card  o   C2PUC6   -   Consumer with Wallet profile performs a checkout with an un -  provisioned card'),
